sub_title: Supporting the Earthquake response in Hatay, Turkey @ IOM WASH/RVO
summary:
Still enjoy combining my two jobs since 2016.

Experienced WASH Specialist with a demonstrated history of working in the civil engineering industry. Strong professional with a Master of Science (MSc) in Civil Engineering and Geosciences, Coastal Engineering at the Technische Universiteit Delft (TU Delft), the Netherlands.

Assistant trainer/coach with Team Jumbo-Visma speedskating. Special interest in improving technical skills of our skaters and particularly their corners thanks to my shorttrack speedskating background.
